{"tid":1411814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"封馬路/隧道 應唔應該放出一個去車位","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:41:24.000Z","uid":64810,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1a661a508bf0e4614a9cf0791e38b4fcf333ecb6","tid":1411814,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"今日見到元朗見到有手足比人撞<br />\n我諗 我地係咪應該放一條細路比車行<br />\n因為今日見人封紅隧 班貸車佬衝出黎拆路障 前後都係封左一陣到<br />\n同埋有好多中間派見到你地一刀切咁封死哂係極反感<br />\n你地開一氣細路一黎可以繼續帶光環 二黎都係極有阻塞既力度<br />\n7婆已經話每日開記者會搞9我地 分化中間派<br />\n民意一轉 我地都玩唔落去"},{"pid":"72fea53deea15ecfc5dd768c1ef9671fa253c03a","tid":1411814,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74376d8fa30f8c57e23bc065b6288f4d7e93ed4d","tid":1411814,"uid":242724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該，唔係冇路俾你行，冇得嘈"},{"pid":"997313ffd068cc031d5b65d7bb9f76c5072ac8b3","tid":1411814,"uid":1435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"贊成<br />\n司機唔係塞死有得郁就唔敢貿貿然落車"},{"pid":"3da5180a700faa32beadcb5f2ecd43485f10fc27","tid":1411814,"uid":7168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放<br />\n塞晒佢地會落車拆<br />\n得番一條路佢地會係果一條路過 之後道開始塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"20426a40cc8eb1593f5b4adaea0788e513d7f3b9","tid":1411814,"uid":195211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"f7d1f2d074923fa0f7fe97eee96ed11bd210b9d8","tid":1411814,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"